          to demonstrate how body text appesectionng Poppins.
        </p>
        <p class='text-sm text-text-50 italic'>
          This is secondary text in Poppins using <code>--color-text-50</code>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Typography Nunito Sans -->
    <section class='font-nunito bg-white p-6 rounded shadow'>
      <h2
        class='text-2xl font-semibold mb-6 border-b pb-2 border-[--color-border-50]'>
        Typography â€“ Nunito
